### Paper Detective - API Integration Test Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@paperId = 1
@apiToken =Bearer YOUR_API_TOKEN_HERE

###############################################################################
### INTELLIGENCE BRIEF API TESTS
###############################################################################

### Test 1.1.1: Generate Intelligence Brief - Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paperId": 1,
  "pdfText": "This is a sample academic paper text. It contains research about artificial intelligence and machine learning. The paper presents a novel approach to neural network architecture that improves performance on image recognition tasks. Our method achieves 95% accuracy on the benchmark dataset.",
  "highlights": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "paperId": 1,
      "pageNumber": 1,
      "text": "novel approach to neural network architecture",
      "priority": "critical",
      "color": "red",
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 100, "width": 200, "height": 20 },
      "timestamp": "2026-02-11T10:00:00Z",
      "createdAt": "2026-02-11T10:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "forceRegenerate": false
}

###

### Test 1.1.2: Missing paperId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pdfText": "Sample text",
  "highlights": []
}

###

### Test 1.1.3: Invalid paperId type
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paperId": "invalid",
  "pdfText": "Sample text",
  "highlights": []
}

###

### Test 1.1.4: Empty pdfText
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paperId": 1,
  "pdfText": "",
  "highlights": []
}

###

### Test 1.1.5: Invalid highlights format
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paperId": 1,
  "pdfText": "Sample text",
  "highlights": "not an array"
}

###

### Test 1.2.1: Retrieve Cached Brief
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief?paperId=1

###

### Test 1.2.2: Retrieve Non-existent Brief
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief?paperId=99999

###

### Test 1.2.3: Invalid paperId Parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief?paperId=invalid

###

### Test 1.3.1: Delete Cached Brief
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief?paperId=1

###

### Test 1.3.2: Delete Non-existent Brief
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/intelligence-brief?paperId=99999

###

